examples.en: He had dirt under his fingernails.
He nervously gnawed on his fingernails.
Her fingernails were bitten to the quick.
She has a nasty habit of biting her fingernails.
She tried to claw his face with her fingernails.
She scraped her fingernails across the blackboard.
For reasons of hygiene, we had to cut our fingernails really short.
